<P>THE <HI>Pre&s;ent State</HI> OF <HI>GENO&V;A,</HI> WITH THE ARTICLES OF THE Treaty of Ce&s;&s;ion TO THE FRENCH KING, AND An Account of the late ACTIONS of the <HI>French</HI> Fleet, before it, and of the Damages there &s;u&s;tain'd by the Bombs and Carca&s;&s;es.</P>
<P>To which is added, A LETTER from the Republick of <HI>Genoua</HI> to the City of <HI>Argiers</HI> upon that Subject.</P>
<P><HI>LONDON:</HI> Printed for <HI>Randall Taylor</HI> near <HI>Stationers-Hall.</HI> 1687.</P>
