</LIST></P>
<P>And among&s;t the Families of the new Nobility, there are four Chief, which vie in Quality
<PB N="89" REF="47"> with tho&s;e of the Ancient; and the&s;e are</P>
<P>The
<LIST>
<ITEM><HI>Ju&s;tiniani,</HI></ITEM>
